<template>
    <v-container>
        <v-toolbar flat>
            <v-toolbar-title >
                <v-btn text @click="redirectHome()">
                    Survey Manager
                </v-btn>
            </v-toolbar-title>
            <v-spacer></v-spacer>
            <v-toolbar-items>
                <v-btn text @click="redirectLogin()">
                    Login
                </v-btn>
                <v-btn text @click="redirectRegister()">
                    Register
                </v-btn>
            </v-toolbar-items>
        </v-toolbar>
    </v-container>
</template>
<script>
export default {
    name: 'Header',
    methods: {
        redirectLogin(){
            this.$router.push('/login')
        },
        redirectRegister(){
            this.$router.push('/register')
        },
        redirectHome(){
            this.$router.push('/')
        }
    }
}
</script>
